  - mf.dashboard
  - mf.orders
  - mf.products
  - mf.pos
  - mf.returns
  - mf.helpcenter
  - mf.aipulse


============================================================
5) ADMIN CONTROLS (REQUIRED)
============================================================
Already implemented
- Store portal filter + bulk set portal (Vendor/Manufuture)
- Subscription packages: `is_manufuture` flag + inline toggle on package list

Next admin enhancements (optional)
- Admin MF dashboard KPIs across all manufuture stores
- Admin store details page: portal badge + quick switch


============================================================
6) DEFINITION OF DONE (MVP)
============================================================
MVP is complete when:
- Vendor Manufuture users see MF layout + MF dashboard with real KPIs
- Orders list works with filters and correct store scoping
- Products list shows real items and stock status
- Normal vendors cannot access MF routes
- Admin can control portal + which packages appear in Manufuture apply

